{"tid":1717084,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"再返唔到工好大劑","createTime":"2019-11-13T13:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T14:19:40.000Z","uid":289842,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"35149ef3975c84bb4f3c17482d00463fbfe46e39","tid":1717084,"uid":289842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"大埔友一名，正宗港豬。係大埔無巴士無火車嘅情況下，我有試過朝早6點幾出巴士站踫下運氣，企左半粒鐘後無奈通知膠層返唔到。諗住大把同事一樣，薯不知，有人千辛萬苦轉幾輪車都要返工。膠層突然話好感激有同事係九龍塘行返旺角，吓....唔通佢想我學下個同事，定串緊我唔夠誠意？平時老細已經唔多like 我，我好驚，如果聴日又係得我，咁會點呀？"},{"pid":"76770efd181d6c223772ae986333abb8afbe0a83","tid":1717084,"uid":292624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"依加開始行返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2789c52709f176d0f069c067b949e84eabc88502","tid":1717084,"uid":74869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76770efd181d6c223772ae986333abb8afbe0a83","tid":1717084,"uid":292624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"依加開始行返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"認同"},{"pid":"61376bcd9dc7b3f37658ab1526bad7f2cbf506bd","tid":1717084,"uid":335357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:44:43.000Z","msg":"［14/11］聽日記得塞埋大欖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1717012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1717012</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e113a61dbf957eb4d604f4dfbef3707d519445f9","tid":1717084,"uid":835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:45:06.000Z","msg":"無工咪搵第份"},{"pid":"396e25c9a76bc3423f61972506e46a1a5a46a797","tid":1717084,"uid":56046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76770efd181d6c223772ae986333abb8afbe0a83","tid":1717084,"uid":292624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"依加開始行返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\"